[FILE:247:descriptions/desc.single]
LDoc is intended to be compatible with LuaDoc and thus follows the pattern 
set by the various *Doc tools. It is designed to give better diagnostics 
than LuaDoc. LDoc also works with Lua C extension code, and provides some 
convenient shortcuts.


